_sText:
Terrorist and Counter Terrorist engage in hostility in the dust market area.

The weapons layout is similar to the original poolday, except with an added galil. All custom material is zipped into the map, all you need is the .bsp.

Map, custom props, textures by 
Slip/Eggs.
